Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:04.17,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A racing second hand, a glittering galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:07.84,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts dried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:11.18,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today's case has a crazy secret\Nbehind a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:12.82,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.70,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.89,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:42.21,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Genta, Mitsuhiko, Ayumi, and I\Nwere playing Kick-the-Can,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:45.54,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}but soon found ourselves having lunch at a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:49.65,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}with Two-Mix vocalist, Minami Takayama-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:56.85,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}She had snuck out to look for her missing partner, Shiina Nagano-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:04.79,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But at the restaurant, she was kidnapped before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:11.40,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The kidnappers demanded\Nthe bag she left at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:15.47,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What's more, they demanded that {\i1}we{\i0} take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:19.81,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It appeared they were after a Two-Mix demo tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:26.32,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}After taking the bag as ordered, the kidnappers contacted us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:32.76,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and said to lose the officers and have Ayumi deliver the tape alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:36.19,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't put Ayumi in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.82,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So, I devised a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.71,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Good work, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:57.84,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There aren't any cops around, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there doesn't seem to be anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.92,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:05.45,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ready to come, like I told ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my hardest!
